text: Rushana Nurjavova (born June 22, 1994) is a Turkmen judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 57 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the first round by Hedvig Karakas. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Turkmenistan female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Turkmenistan Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics
